OL,3,CPost Office will release postage
OL,4,Cstamps to celebrate musician Maurice
OL,5,CGibb CBE
OL,7,FThe Post Office (IOMPO) will release a
OL,8,Fset of eight postage stamps to
OL,9,Fcelebrate Douglas born musician
OL,10,FMaurice Gibb CBE.
OL,12,FThe stamps will feature images of
OL,13,FMaurice, with some taken by
OL,14,Faccomplished photographer Guido Karp -
OL,15,Fthe First Day Cover will be launched
OL,16,Fon 29 February.
OL,18,FThe occasion will be only the second
OL,19,Ftime in IMOPO's 50 year history that
OL,20,Fthey have released a postal tribute.
