OL,7,FMaurice founded the pop-rock group,
OL,8,Fthe Bee Gees, with younger fraternal
OL,9,Ftwin Robin Gibb and younger brother
OL,10,FSir Barry Gibb. Maurice who was born
OL,11,Fon 22 December 1949, passed away in
OL,12,F2003.
OL,14,FHe played a key role in the group's
OL,15,Fsuccess as a multi-instrumentalist and
OL,16,Fvocalist.
