OL,7,FThe Bee Gees' iconic success was
OL,8,Fmarked by hits like "Stayin' Alive"
OL,9,Fand "How Deep Is Your Love,"
OL,10,Fsolidified their status as music
OL,11,Flegends, forging Maurice's legacy in
OL,12,Fmusical history.
OL,14,FHis son, Adam Gibb, said: "My dad has
OL,15,Falways been very proud of his Manx
OL,16,Froots and it is an honour that his
OL,17,Flife and career are now commemorated
OL,18,Fwith this wonderful set of stamps.
