OL,7,F"I'm sure he would be delighted with
OL,8,Fthe collection and we are grateful
OL,9,Fthat the collection will support
OL,10,FNordoff Robbins, a charity that was
OL,11,Fvery close to my dad and his brothers."
OL,13,FThe stamps will support Nordoff
OL,14,FRobbins, a charity who investigates
OL,15,Fthe impact that music therapy has for
OL,16,Fpeople affected by life`limiting
OL,17,Fillness, isolation or disability.
