OL,5,CGibb CBE
OL,7,FGuido Karp, photographer who loved
OL,8,Fworking with the Bee Gees, said: "We
OL,9,Fhad a real bond. Their kindness and
OL,10,Fmusic made a huge impression on me. I
OL,11,Fcaptured my last photo with the band
OL,12,Fin 2001. Losing Maurice was such a
OL,13,Fblow to the world.
OL,15,F"The Bee Gees hold a special place for
OL,16,Fme both professionally and personally.
OL,17,FMaurice's untimely death in 2003 left
OL,18,Fbehind a legacy of much loved music
OL,19,Fand memories and I am honoured to see
OL,20,Fmy images reproduced in this postal
OL,21,Ftribute."
