OL,7,FGuido Karp captured the photographs
OL,8,Fduring the 1991 'High Civilization
OL,9,FWorld Tour', which was the Bee Gees'
OL,10,Ftenth concert tour in support of their
OL,11,Fnineteenth studio album 'High
OL,12,FCivilization'.
OL,14,FKarp has also contributed to the issue
OL,15,Ftext along with recording engineer
OL,16,FJohn Merchant, who worked with the Bee
OL,17,FGees on a number of their hit albums,
OL,18,Fincluding 'High Civilisation'.
