OL,7,FMaxine Cannon, General Manager of Isle
OL,8,Fof Man Stamps & Coins, said: "It is a
OL,9,Fgreat pleasure to pay tribute to
OL,10,FMaurice Gibb CBE. Guido Karp's
OL,11,Fstunning images, recording engineer
OL,12,FJohn Merchant's insights and working
OL,13,Fclosely with the family and Adam in
OL,14,Fparticular, has made this postal
OL,15,Ftribute a very enjoyable experience.
OL,17,F"We are very grateful for all the
OL,18,Fsupport we have received and very
OL,19,Fproud of the final results."
